SAUCER SHOOT

Final version of Saucer Shoot game from Dragonfly tutorial.

To build:

0) Make sure you have appropriate development environment.
See: http://dragonfly.wpi.edu/engine/ for details.

1) Modify Makefile as appropriate for platform
+ Uncommend PLATFORM line if on cygwin
+ Set INCPATH to point to location of Dragonfly include files
+ Set ENG to point to location of Dragonfly engine

2) Type "make depend" to build appropriate dependencies

3) Type "make clean" to remove any stale files

4) Type "make" to build

5) Type "game" to run

Happy shooting!
